{"type": "article", "id": 62201, "title": "这把诞生 70 年的座椅重新推出，新加入了软垫版本｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-19T22:41:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 2059, "name": "插画"}, {"id": 57365, "name": "found/Founded"}, {"id": 57366, "name": "Deesawat"}, {"id": 57367, "name": "Masaya"}, {"id": 9086, "name": "Starbucks"}, {"id": 47966, "name": "Carl Hansen & Son"}, {"id": 57368, "name": "Tishk Barzanji"}, {"id": 57369, "name": "Apiwat Chitapanya"}, {"id": 57370, "name": "Børge Mogensen"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/201903192154385uXh2F8HsmPONKJd.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: #101010} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #101010} span.s8 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #101010; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #101010} </style>  </p><h3>Contour Chair by Børge Mogensen for Carl Hansen &amp; Son </h3><p>Contour 椅是丹麦设计师 Børge Mogensen 的代表作，它于 1949 年在哥本哈根高级木工协会家具展览上首次亮相，最近由丹麦设计品牌 Carl Hansen &amp; Son 重新推出，加入了全新的软垫版本。</p><p>在设计 Contour Chair 时，Mogensen 不再采用一贯的实木材质，转而尝试了压制木饰面，这一材质和技术为当时的实验风格和设计开创了新的可能性。</p><p>Contour Chair 拥有实木框架、完一坚固的木制框架, 有角度的腿和弯曲和向后倾斜的单板座椅。靠背赋予了这把椅款独特的外形，纤细、压制薄板的壳体结构上有两个自然镂空结构，将其牢牢地固定在座椅上。</p><p>“靠背上的镂空既具有装饰性又有助于将木饰面弯曲至恰到好处的形状。圆形靠背适合各类坐姿。椅子相对较低，让它呈现出休闲舒适的美感。通过这种方式，Mogensen 成功地设计出一款体积相对较小，但又十分舒适的椅款，”Knud Erik Hansen 说。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215544MIDPVGJOhF6orcUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.763281\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215545xI2mNSgEGHrpROXM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215545fkGJV7OR92cTQr6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215545ILe52iys8bJT4XC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903192155461KifeIgDurhT2EmQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215546R6kSYF5ZxX4h7sif.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.479688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215546nUvKCcZo5wGXrs2d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.337500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.carlhansen.com/en/inspiration/news/contour-chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">Carl Hansen &amp; Son</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Mini Starbucks Coffee Shop Models</h3><p>虽然咖啡不是每个人都喜爱的饮品，但是对很多都市人来说是不可缺少，香港星巴克定期都会推出不同新饮品。</p><p>最近推出的六款新商品，将樱花最优雅的姿态描绘在各款咖啡杯、随行杯及水樽上。另外更同步推出一套三款的迷你星巴克分店模型，在办公室或是书桌上营造一个小小咖啡世界。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215652ydHj7NfUsDziJobt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Stick Screen by Apiwat Chitapanya &amp; Deesawat &amp; Masaya</h3><p>设计师 Apiwat Chitapanya 最近与两家泰国公司 Deesawat 和 Masaya 合作，准备在今年的米兰设计周期间推出一款装饰性屏风 Stick Screen。</p><p>这是用两种不同材料做成的柚木屏风，呈几何图案，搭配模仿泰国北部山脉的有机形状的黄铜基座，灵感来自大树上的树枝所产生的阴影。每一个屏风组合在一起，形成一个视觉上充满活力的作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215741b4FrNzEn9tJHhdwU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215742a5H2wX0n9myMzuIj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903192157424I8WGSMOrzVdoZKq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665432\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215742uTtyP5qBM79S4nlF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.503125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215742KEXncyF2eAxtjdZQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215742fhkXYwL5p0R4lrmg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.579012\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215742K495nZqav0kBdJMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.503125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215743XmvIk3DqCjrKaEMJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.460494\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-geometric-stick-screen-born-from-a-collaboration-between-two-thai-companies/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cube Heater by found/Founded</h3><p>Cube 是一款立方体加热器，出自韩国创意设计工作室 found/Founded 之手，造型紧凑、便携、现代且简洁，可以与任何风格的家居环境匹配。</p><p>它没有单独的电源按钮，用户可以使用模拟转盘调节功率和加热器强度。Cube 以哑光色调为主，包括木炭黑、白色、蓝色和绿色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215840teYdic0AjTJmG69O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215840KxSkj25LvwATnNG7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903192158410zHbhOg1UYTWoRj4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215841ilduOIFzx4wYCD12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319215841IBo2q01D7m9sVUSC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903192158395LZB7aK13fOWtYCQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.foundfounded.com/cube\" rel=\"nofollow\">found/Founded</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Psychedelic Architectural illustrations by Tishk Barzanji</h3><p>伦敦艺术家 Tishk Barzanji 从 2016 年开始，在其 instagram 平台分享其辨识度极高的插画作品，尝试唤醒公众对建筑的批判性思考。</p><p>在他的电子版插画中，他通过借鉴那些创造了梦境般的、超现实主义的宇宙的参考资料，探索了现代建筑的元素，营造出了一种简朴而又令人不安的氛围。</p><p>他那些难懂的几何图形，黑人或红色的小比例人居住在其中，他们总是以运动的方式呈现，就好像他们在被冻结的那一刻还活着。Barzanji 解释了他的创造过程：“我的作品灵感来自于古代历史、现代运动以及我在 1997 年搬到这里后在伦敦的经历。我的创作过程处理空间、颜色、解构、边界的破坏，理解这个移动世界中的生活空间，以及这些空间内的人们的互动。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319220003p5XyqimZF4MvlQuk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319220004o0lP7EYIWOjtQdV4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319220006rB5skWGiZRtCE9JP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319220007x3pJaVzFkfZMQ0CR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319220008Xm9nifQEU1ru8R0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319220009PqtSuyGrX6slKoxi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190319220009LXRxnDGSOBliZauf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/03/19/tishk-barzanji-architectural-illustrations/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}